{
  "stem": "24885.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's gone back that's what my cousin was telling me that that's what happened in Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This-- this is a lot of baloney that they tell you-- only the SS did it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It took a lot of other ones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I'll tell you another fact-- civilians to participate-- otherwise, they couldn't have never accomplished.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, it was much easier for them on Polish territory to do it because the Poles are anti-Semites from way back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was going on, and then the end of '40 they started the ghetto, which meant Jews lived in a 10-kilometer area they squeeze us into two or three.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My sister and her husband and child moved in with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't have large quarters to start with, but we brought in another family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we managed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In '41, we realized-- one morning we woke up we saw a lot of artillery, bus, trucks, and horse and wagon moving towards the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Right away-- I don't remember the month when that-- right away we knew that they were attacking Russia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it turned out in a few weeks later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now there we heard more cruel stories, shortly thereafter, of what the Ukrainians, the Lithuanians did to the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And a lot of our people who escaped-- younger people, before the Germans came in, escaped towards Russia-- were caught in this melee.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was terrible in there, so we understood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But we were sitting in Radom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We didn't see anything, it didn't affect us, but otherwise nobody told you anything what was happening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "A few months later, it's also in '41, one night they came down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were looking for communists.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Came with a list of names.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was past midnight.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
